'From Squeak2.9alpha of 16 June 2000 [latest update: #2426] on 21 June 2000 at 12:55:43 pm'!"Change Set:		FullScreenPref-zLDate:			21 June 2000Author:			Lantz RowlandFor 2.9alpha onlyAdded a windows preference to optionally take advantage of the margin inset of the SystemWindow #fullScreen that Stefan added in 2419FullScreenSysWin-sma .	- Add #fullScreenLeavesDeskMargins preference 	- Chg SystemWindow fullScreen	- - - -	((Preferences useGlobalFlaps			and: [CurrentProjectRefactoring currentFlapsSuppressed not])		or: [Preferences fullScreenLeavesDeskMargins])	- - - -	- Postscript Preferences absorbAdditions .The ScrollPane messages are untouched but they did not want to be left behind .Lantz "!!Preferences class methodsFor: 'help' stamp: 'zL 6/21/2000 12:32'!helpMsgsAdditionwindowsfullScreenLeavesDeskMargins	^ #(#(#fullScreenLeavesDeskMargins 'If true, a Full Screen request to a Window to will leave margins around it. If false, the Window will fill the Screen unless the Global Flaps are showing.') )"Preferences initializeHelpMessages"! !!Preferences class methodsFor: 'standard preferences' stamp: 'zL 6/21/2000 12:34'!fullScreenLeavesDeskMargins	"Preferences fullScreenLeavesDeskMargins  	Leave desktop space with margins set in SystemWindow #fullScreen"	^ self valueOfFlag: #fullScreenLeavesDeskMargins! !!Preferences class methodsFor: 'initial values' stamp: 'zL 6/21/2000 12:32'!initialValuesAdditionwindowsfullScreenLeavesDeskMargins	^ #(#(#fullScreenLeavesDeskMargins #true #(#windows)) )"Preferences initializeAddedPreferences"! !!ScrollPane methodsFor: 'access' stamp: 'LC 6/12/2000 09:28'!retractableScrollBar	^ retractableScrollBar! !!ScrollPane methodsFor: 'access' stamp: 'LC 6/12/2000 09:28'!scrollBarOnLeft	^ scrollBarOnLeft! !!SystemWindow methodsFor: 'menu' stamp: 'zL 6/21/2000 12:35'!fullScreen	"SystemWindow fullScreen	Zoom Window to Full World size with possible DeskMargins"	| left right possibleBounds |	left _ right _ 0.	self paneMorphs		do: [:pane | ((pane isKindOf: ScrollPane)					and: [pane retractableScrollBar])				ifTrue: [pane scrollBarOnLeft						ifTrue: [left _ left max: pane scrollbarWidth]						ifFalse: [right _ right max: pane scrollbarWidth]]].	possibleBounds _ self worldBounds				insetBy: (left @ 0 corner: right @ 0).	((Preferences useGlobalFlaps				and: [CurrentProjectRefactoring currentFlapsSuppressed not])			or: [Preferences fullScreenLeavesDeskMargins])		ifTrue: [possibleBounds _ possibleBounds insetBy: 22].	self bounds: possibleBounds! !"Postscript:Absorb new #fullScreenLeavesDeskMargins ."Preferences absorbAdditions . !